//   "MSize"       : Support Maximum Size in mm
//   "ISize"       : Support Interior Size in mm
//   "AAngle"      : Support Angle in Â°
//   "YDirection"  : Support Y direction (Abutment)
//   "EHeights"    : Equalize heights (Abutment)
